sentences:
AIDAblu is a Sphinx - class cruise ship , operated by the German cruise line , AIDA Cruises .
AIDAblu is the seventh ship in the cruise line .
The vessel was delivered by Meyer Werft to its owners last 4 February 2010 .
She is a sister ship to AIDAdiva , AIDAbella , AIDAluna with a half deck more , and is followed by similar AIDAsol and AIDAmar .
She has a passenger capacity of 2,050 .
The name of AIDAblu had been used for a former AIDA ship from 2004 - 2007 .
AIDA Cruises ' parent company , Carnival Corporation & plc , then transferred the ship to another cruise line .
, Ocean Village , and was renamed Ocean Village Two .
In 2009 , Ocean Village Two was again transferred to another cruise line , P&O ; Cruises Australia , also a Carnival daughter company , and was renamed Pacific Jewel .
